    Hello, [% lang %] world!
[% END -%]
    [%- foo() -%]
    Hello, [% lang %] world!
T
    Hello, TTerse world!
    Hello, Xslate world!
X

    # http://github.com/gfx/p5-Text-Xslate/issues#issue/9
    [<<'T', <<'X', 'issue #9'],
